{"tid":419694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"身邊有冇朋友由黃絲轉咗做警犬?","createTime":"2017-09-30T16:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T15:37:17.000Z","uid":114220,"like":432,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"364dde6afbfe9568382e1d663bfcba86c766f847","tid":419694,"uid":114220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"話說雨革嗰陣又話自己日日出去幫手<br />\n咩幫手搬運物資,俾人打又乜乜77<br />\n轉個撚頭做咗警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實政府做嘅只係好簡單<br />\n毅進仔出到嚟社會搵唔到咩錢<br />\n普通pc仔一入職2萬幾<br />\n係人都撲倒去維護呢個體制<br />\n有冇巴打身邊朋友都變成咁?"},{"pid":"37391bcc866eef8b68dc388c2f7dfcd6b017841a","tid":419694,"uid":7452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:53:10.000Z","msg":"卜[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/005301_cc1ea93f919d154e67d4b2d2f121e8be.jpg[/img］\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F005301_cc1ea93f919d154e67d4b2d2f121e8be.jpg%5B%2Fimg%EF%BC%BD&d=wP3koozxvDs1WiWs1vL7wsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b012ba24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/005301_cc1ea93f919d154e67d4b2d2f121e8be.jpg[/img］</a>"},{"pid":"be9e6e92fe5c7211eec9656d32098999a60d63b5","tid":419694,"uid":7452,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/005330_245c195af6094a340ca413768a7a186b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F005330_245c195af6094a340ca413768a7a186b.jpg&h=dab668bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55efe82ac5681b9829231293394272967590cdfc","tid":419694,"uid":7452,"like":143,"dislike":2,"score":141,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:55:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/005330_245c195af6094a340ca413768a7a186b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l