img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黃絲普遍學歷高過藍，應該多d考督察<br />\n警犬除左有武力，更重要嘅係情報，而且人工高<br />\n革命講到尾都係錢，d錢你自己唔攞就益左對家，關鍵時刻你唔出面都可以出錢<br />\n滲透唔係一時三刻嘅事，當年辛亥革命都係靠滲透新軍先有武裝<br />\n至於洗腦嘅野，你又要革命又唔信人，咁你想點先？革命就係團結一切可團結嘅力量先會成功，唔係靠自己一個打曬</blockquote><br />\n重點係骨氣問題，兩三年前就話黑警死全家，依家就為人工為穩定去做<br />\n我就唔信依班友可靠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人既''核心價值''只係搵錢同自身利益</blockquote><br />\n骨氣食得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你既骨氣都只係值啲既人工咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6538897ba3aeb9ae829630011db7f0eec2e82f","tid":419694,"uid":66457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:50:59.000Z","msg":"大把"},{"pid":"a950e9fb86dc7cb5414250054c2ce25b48269cee","tid":419694,"uid":623,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:51:41.000Z","msg":"人會大會成熟，唔通仲好似你班傻仔咁腦荀未生埋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2332870f119320baca32a2b9d0d9c3e68d6a2b95","tid":419694,"uid":84579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:57:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>私人市場咁撚閪<br />\n係人都想入正苦啦<br />\n毅進仔除左做警察<br />\n唔會有其他工有三皮</blockquote><br />\n都係果句啦，正苦工唔一定要做紀律部隊，紀律部隊亦都唔係得警察"},{"pid":"273c28879d13902cff0b864142ca6fd5fd8ba99d","tid":419694,"uid":878,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/005330_245c195af6094a340ca413768a7a186b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F005330_245c195af6094a340ca413768a7a186b.jpg&h=dab668bd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n林sir 係好例子<br />\nBand3仔出生 dse單位數字<br />\nFacebook掛黃屍icon 點知還是逃不過比人tag既post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只係希望第時再有大型活動發生<br />\n呢啲人可以輕手啲 <br />\n心中留有公道<br />\n唔好忘記昔日自己都係一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地只係一班冇思想嘅羊群<br />\n啱啱中學畢業身邊個個話政府有問題<br />\n聽晒人地講乜就信乜出黎佔領<br />\n事後冇嘢做 知到政府工穩定人工高<br />\n就去做警犬<br />\n然後身邊啲伙計 對上嗰班三柴同幫辦<br />\n都日日洗腦話要維穩 反政府等如賤人<br />\n班人冇獨立思考 根本枉為人"},{"pid":"f314df46f1c562f655e32f34ab770961630afbd8","tid":419694,"uid":63997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:08:57.000Z","msg":"可以黃絲入去伏卧_<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19d39bc85902565ce249b2cfc6cad0d93d2b60d","tid":419694,"uid":14191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:33:24.000Z","msg":"識人係咁<br />\n做完警犬之後立場即變<br />\n句句都屌黃絲<br />\n<br />\n讀唔到書就係咁"},{"pid":"4199e88016a53a789b3a13cd06bca93f26e9d875","tid":419694,"uid":6435,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/005330_245c195af6094a340ca413768a7a186b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F005330_245c195af6094a340ca413768a7a186b.jpg&h=dab668bd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n林sir 係好例子<br />\nBand3仔出生 dse單位數字<br />\nFacebook掛黃屍icon 點知還是逃不過比人tag既post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只係希望第時再有大型活動發生<br />\n呢啲人可以輕手啲 <br />\n心中留有公道<br />\n唔好忘記昔日自己都係一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咪ON9<br />\n呢D人要表忠誠先打得最撚狼死"},{"pid":"88f629a641986b2c6b381c8afef2817d51b4b4f1","tid":419694,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:43:30.000Z","msg":"係警隊做緊卧底"},{"pid":"eb93a48f6411a504cbfda36a89faad92f01c9a2a","tid":419694,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:46:01.000Z","msg":"係內部收風,睇下有冇咩爆"},{"pid":"8da2beb9ec9c98460d13f3c44190a793343134a5","tid":419694,"uid":72943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"好多黃絲朋友入左去做警察<br />\n仲好理智 但聽講岩岩入去成堆老屎忽都好似洗腦"},{"pid":"bc711db03b4fca6938a859b2a85364973105ff23","tid":419694,"uid":114220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人會大會成熟，唔通仲好似你班傻仔咁腦荀未生埋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果成熟係會令你為虎作倀<br />\n閣下嘅成熟程度真係令人不敢恭維"},{"pid":"f3878a9aa25ce9ca9d5aec7c27a1826def45d7fa","tid":419694,"uid":82409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:51:30.000Z","msg":"一方面係社會既悲哀 一方面係香港人既低劣人性<br />\n<br />\n利申 死警渣 死全家"},{"pid":"c46d157bb94a0e1bbc8c88469dc7641388080e76","tid":419694,"uid":143400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:52:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雖然唔撚識上面個黑警<br />\n但祝佢同佢全家<br />\n長命百歲 百病纏身<br />\n老婆外遇 紅杏出牆<br />\n全家愛滋 性器潰爛<br />\n早日喪子 孤獨終老</blockquote><br />\n所有睇到依個post 嘅黑警 見者有份 永不落空</blockquote><br />\n睇唔到都有份，人人有份，永不落空。<br />\n警犬比狗更低賤"},{"pid":"f656ba9d769fe0b71427a5a0354a089b98627ce3","tid":419694,"uid":34793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:01:08.000Z","msg":"呢個post好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇上連登一排搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acaf2d677f266b2bcce06e6ac9eade0d67ced3aa","tid":419694,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:01:36.000Z","msg":"你班毒撚傻下傻下做唔到"},{"pid":"ad283cbb320d6d54718dfae6bbf33b9051073d8f","tid":419694,"uid":9284,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:16:07.000Z","msg":"大把啦 <br />\n有個做督察  我就面試fail左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824ecb973814d6db1a6a